      <title>佐治亚州恢复引发抗议的“外国代理人”法</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-03/georgia-revives-foreign-agent-law-that-sparked-protests</link>
      <description><![CDATA[格鲁吉亚执政党表示，正在重启一项针对“外国特工”的法律草案，该法律草案去年引发了警察和抗议者之间的暴力冲突，并让人将其与俄罗斯用来镇压批评者的措施进行比较。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-03/georgia-revives-foreign-agent-law-that-sparked-protests</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Apr 2024 12:16:09 GMT</pubDate>
